ENTRY       EC 1.1.1.52                 Enzyme
NAME        3alpha-hydroxycholanate dehydrogenase;
            alpha-hydroxy-cholanate dehydrogenase
CLASS       Oxidoreductases;
            Acting on the CH-OH group of donors;
            With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
SYSNAME     lithocholate:NAD+ oxidoreductase
REACTION    lithocholate + NAD+ = 3-oxo-5beta-cholan-24-oate + NADH + H+ [RN:R04139]
