            NAD+ [CPD:C00003]
PRODUCT     3-oxo-5beta-cholan-24-oate;
            NADH [CPD:C00004];
            H+ [CPD:C00080]
COMMENT     Also acts on other 3alpha-hydroxysteroids with an acidic side-chain.
